e given by an upper bound on the regularity of its\npoints.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2015 16:00:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2016 08:26:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 19 Jul 2018 08:29:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-23"}
