 bonding and incipient ferroelectricity.\nThis demonstrates the importance of electronic states near the band edges in\ndetermining the equilibrium structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2015 19:48:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-12"}
