\\varepsilon^2)$ samples in ${\\rm poly}_k(1/\\varepsilon)$-time, removing\nthe quasi-polynomial dependence of the running time on $1/\\varepsilon$ from the\nalgorithm of Daskalakis, Kamath, and Tzamos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2015 20:27:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2016 05:02:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-17"}
