ts the\nproperties of the rare earth ions located in nanoparticles. Moreover, some\nkinds of nanocrystals can play as effective rare earth sensitizers.\nFabrication, assessment and application of glass-ceramic photonic systems,\nespecially waveguides, deserve an appropriate discussion which is the aim of\nthis paper, focused on luminescent glass-ceramics. In this work, a brief\nhistorical review, consolidated results and recent advances in this important\nscientific and technological area will be presented, and some perspectives will\nbe outlined.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Nov 2015 10:44:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-13"}
